  <brief_title>A Pilot Study to Determine a Candidate Protocol for Transcranial Electrical Stimulation in the Treatment of Anxiety</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimizing Transcranial Electrical Stimulation for Clinical Applications (the OptES Study): A Pilot Study to Determine a Candidate Protocol for Treatment of Anxiety (OptES-Anx)</official_title>
